Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.75,0:30:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Janice Japan.\NYou're going to sign I got to sign all these.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.14,0:30:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yep.\N>> I sat next to Janice Japan at the Fillmore East many a
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.94,0:30:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,year ago.\NJanice was sitting right next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.57,0:30:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and she was drinking Southern Comfort.\NShe we were in the first row.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.11,0:30:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway,\Nthen it came time she played with Big Brother in the
