Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.02,0:30:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So she went up on stage did uh >> ball\Nand chain >> ball and chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.75,0:30:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When she did ball and chain in the middle of ball\Nand chain there's a long hesitation
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.72,0:30:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,where the music stops\Nand the whole crowd just went insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.02,0:31:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They they they were just like in a hypnotic state.\NAnd then after this long silence, she hits this high note.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.24,0:31:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang.\NAfter this long silence
