Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.40,0:31:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and screamed with joy and happiness.\NThat was Janice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.72,0:31:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N>> God bless her.
