Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.14,0:31:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yeah.\N>> Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.99,0:31:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Um Dr.\NHawkins um um I'm one of those people who have been a
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.96,0:31:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,lifelong spiritual student.\NAnd I started as a teenager
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.94,0:31:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and was disciplined sometimes more in life\Nand sometimes less,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.85,0:31:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but nevertheless always very serious about it.\NAnd I would have thought that now
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.90,0:31:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've had my 50th birthday,\NI'd be a little further along than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.63,0:31:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And quite honestly, my question is,\Nhow far can you progress in one life?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.24,0:31:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And is it possible to reach enlightenment in one life?\N>> Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.31,0:32:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And what then?\NWhat did I not do?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.90,0:32:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Who says you're not enlightened?\N>> Who says it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.11,0:32:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I guess me.\N>> You.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.66,0:32:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I saw your chart and I don't meet those numbers.\N>> How would you know whether you're enlightened or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.75,0:32:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd have to be enlightened to know whether you're\Nenlightened or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.83,0:32:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you say you're not enlightened?\NYou expect a mysterious magical phenomena to occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.90,0:32:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A mystical magical phenomena.\N>> Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.43,0:32:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,>> It's enlightened to seek enlightenment, is it not?\N>> One in 10 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.52,0:32:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,," Do you know that it's less than one in 10 million will\Nsay become enlightened?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.50,0:33:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact.\N" So you I want you to appreciate how rare it is in the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.33,0:33:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,first place to even choose such a destiny\Nand you don't know how far you are along the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.21,0:33:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea.\NYou're just looking for certain subjective phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.32,0:33:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhm.\N>> Forget all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.23,0:33:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,>> The difference between being enlightened\Nand unenlightened is 110,000 of a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.62,0:33:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes exactly 1 10,000th of a second to go from an ego\Ndominated state to a non-ego state.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.91,0:33:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes one 10,000 of a second.\NAll of a sudden, you're in a different dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.02,0:34:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.47,0:34:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to s you have to surrender surrender uh your\Nwill to God in the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.52,0:34:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,\NGod doesn't want you enlightened right now
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.21,0:34:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,because you got other things to do\Nand then you get enlightened later
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.14,0:34:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,when it serves God's better purpose.\NYou see?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.86,0:34:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Hello, Dr.\NHawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.99,0:34:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,>> We need you to teach kindergarten right now, you know.\NIt's good to see you both again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.31,0:34:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Enlightened all over the place.\N>> Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.75,0:34:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So, um my question is um based on understanding karma.\NYour your body of work has really helped me understand my
