Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.00,0:34:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Father was drunk every day of my life\Nand there was sexual abuse in my family and that was
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.99,0:34:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that was a very difficult thing for me to comprehend.\NUm,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.64,0:34:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I became an atheist when I learned\Nthat priests molested children.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.89,0:34:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I had a great understanding\Nand epiphany through reading your body of work of how to
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.41,0:35:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,separate God from the predators or the people\Nthat indulge in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.20,0:35:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So now I have a very strong faith in God\Nand all that's fine.
