Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.67,0:35:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, undo it.\N>> Very often what happens is you merely become you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.93,0:35:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,experience what you perpetrate on others.\NThat's been my, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.39,0:35:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that's happened in this lifetime\Nthat I've subjectively experienced really great agony
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.91,0:35:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and that it was equivalent to what I had caused to others.\NThat was the uh full undoing of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.99,0:35:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's all you can do is say, "Well,\NI hope that undoes that negative karma.
