Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.65,0:36:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gone through some, you know, great periods of agony.\NFrankly,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.65,0:36:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that was the undoing of having imposed\Nthat very significant
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.27,0:36:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that specific agony on another human being in another\Nlifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.51,0:36:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So we chose to overcome the hurdle of what we had done in\Nthe past.
