Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.62,1:49:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,about?\NUh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.51,1:50:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel guilty that I don't feel guilty about anything.\NOh, thank you, Lord, for saving me.
